label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":16,"text":"A型疱疹病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":32,"text":"接触性传染病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"急性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":20,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 鸡传染性喉气管炎是由A型疱疹病毒引起的鸡的一种急性，接触性传染病。

label: [{"start":1,"end":5,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":9,"end":16,"text":"咳出血样渗出物","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 以呼吸困难、咳嗽、咳出血样渗出物为特征。

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"喉部和气管黏膜肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"喉部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"气管黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"糜烂","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 喉部和气管黏膜肿胀、出血并形成糜烂。

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"死亡率高","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"产蛋率下降","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 鸡传染性喉气管炎传播快，死亡率高，产蛋率下降，给养鸡业造成重大损失。

label: [{"start":14,"end":15,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":25,"end":28,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (一)流行病学特征：各种日龄鸡均可感染发病，尤其是成年鸡的症状最具有特征性。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":9,"text":"康复后带毒鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 病鸡和康复后带毒鸡是主要传染源。

label: [{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"上呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"眼内","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 自然感染途径以上呼吸道和眼内为主，此外，污染的垫草、用具等也可成为传播媒介；

label: [{"start":48,"end":56,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 种蛋也能传播病毒；饲养管理不良、卫生条件极差，如拥挤、通风不良、冷热不均，尤其夏季高温等均可促进鸡传染性喉气管炎的发生。

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"易感鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":66,"end":67,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":57,"end":65,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡传染性喉气管炎在易感鸡群中传播快，感染率可达90%～100%,死亡率5%~70%不等，一般为10%～20%。耐过鸡传染性喉气管炎的鸡可获得长期免疫力。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"康复鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":38,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 由于康复鸡有的带毒可达2年之久，并随时排毒污染环境，可以引起鸡传染性喉气管炎的再度暴发流行，应引起鸡场重视。

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡传染性喉气管炎一年四季均可发生，但以晚秋、冬、早春和炎热的夏天为主要流行季节。

label: [{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (二)临床症状：自然感染的鸡其潜伏期约为1周左右。

label: [{"start":10,"end":11,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"鸡只","labels":["type"]}]
text: 全群发病初期只见少数鸡出现流泪，并有个别的鸡只突然死亡。

label: [{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":5,"end":10,"text":"急性流行性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":24,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":27,"end":33,"text":"鼻孔有分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"鼻孔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"湿性啰音","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":43,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"喘气","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":51,"end":55,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":56,"end":60,"text":"张口呼吸","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":61,"end":67,"text":"咳出带而黏液","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":71,"end":75,"text":"窒息死亡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":57,"end":58,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 随后鸡群呈急性流行性特征，出现特征性的呼吸道症状，病鸡鼻孔有分泌物，有湿性啰音，有咳嗽、喘气，严重病鸡呼吸困难，张口呼吸，咳出带而黏液，有时会窒息死亡。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"喉部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"喉部黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":28,"text":"喉部黏膜上有淡黄色或带血的凝固物附着","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"淡黄色","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 开口检查喉部时，可见喉部黏膜上有淡黄色或带血的凝固物附着，不易擦去。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"迅速消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"冠髯发紫","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"发紫","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":19,"text":"排绿色稀粪","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"绿色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"衰竭死亡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"冠髯","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":18,"end":19,"text":"粪","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡迅速消瘦，冠髯发紫，有时排绿色稀粪，最后衰竭死亡。

label: [{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"带毒鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 一般病程2周左右，有的逐渐恢复则成为带毒鸡。

label: [{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"生长迟缓","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"产蛋减少","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"流泪","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"结膜炎","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 症状轻微的病鸡只限于生长迟缓，产蛋减少，流泪和结膜炎等症状，多数可于2周内恢复。

label: [{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":11,"end":12,"text":"喙","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":18,"end":23,"text":"带血的黏液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":33,"text":"喉头和气管黏膜肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":45,"end":55,"text":"气管腔内常充满血凝块","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":52,"end":55,"text":"血凝块","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":56,"end":58,"text":"黏液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":59,"end":68,"text":"淡黄色干酪样渗出物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":69,"end":73,"text":"气管栓塞","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":71,"end":73,"text":"栓塞","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":59,"end":62,"text":"淡黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"喉头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"气管黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":45,"end":48,"text":"气管腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":69,"end":71,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (三)病理变化：在病鸡喙的周围常附有带血的黏液，喉头和气管黏膜肿胀、充血、出血，甚至坏死，气管腔内常充满血凝块、黏液、淡黄色干酪样渗出物或气管栓塞。

label: [{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"炎症扩散","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":14,"text":"渗出液出现于气管下部","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"渗出液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"气管下部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":27,"text":"肺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"气囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 有些病鸡渗出液出现于气管下部，并使炎症扩散到支气管、肺和气囊。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"轻症病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":10,"text":"眼结膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":16,"text":"眶下窦上皮","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":18,"text":"眶下窦上皮水肿","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 轻症病鸡只出现眼结膜和眶下窦上皮水肿和充血。

label: [{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"健康鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":61,"end":65,"text":"炎症变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":57,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":58,"end":60,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":35,"text":"泄殖腔黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":48,"end":53,"text":"泄殖腔黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":19,"text":"气管分泌物","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 用小毛刷将可疑的含毒材料(如气管分泌物等)涂擦接种于健康鸡的泄殖腔黏膜上，经24～48小时检查，泄殖腔黏膜出现水肿、充血等炎症变化者，判为阳性反应。

label: [{"start":2,"end":10,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":28,"end":34,"text":"特效治疗药物","labels":["drug"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"西药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"中药","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 治疗鸡传染性喉气管炎的药物有中药、西药多种，但没有一种是特效治疗药物。

label: [{"start":6,"end":11,"text":"对症治疗法","labels":["control"]},{"start":13,"end":22,"text":"用棉拭子或镊子取出","labels":["control"]},{"start":34,"end":39,"text":"涂以碘甘油","labels":["control"]},{"start":36,"end":39,"text":"碘甘油","labels":["drug"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"喉部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 发病后可采取对症治疗法，如用棉拭子或镊子取出病鸡喉部或气管的堵塞物并涂以碘甘油；

label: [{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"红霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"庆大霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"泰乐菌素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"恩诺沙星","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 也可以用红霉素、庆大霉素、泰乐菌素、恩诺沙星等药物治疗，以防细菌继发感染；

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"中成药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"双炎散","labels":["drug"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"喉管宁","labels":["drug"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"喉毒泉","labels":["drug"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"轻症病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 中成药可减缓症状，对轻症病鸡也有治愈希望，如双炎散、喉管宁、喉毒泉等。

label: [{"start":3,"end":9,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":10,"end":18,"text":"改善鸡舍通风条件","labels":["control"]},{"start":19,"end":25,"text":"注意环境卫生","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"不引进病鸡","labels":["control"]},{"start":33,"end":41,"text":"严格执行消毒制度","labels":["control"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 平时要加强饲养管理，改善鸡舍通风条件，注意环境卫生，不引进病鸡，并严格执行消毒制度等综合防制措施。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"免疫接种","labels":["control"]},{"start":19,"end":25,"text":"用弱毒苗点眼","labels":["control"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"眼","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"鼻","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"弱毒苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"滴鼻免疫","labels":["control"]}]
text: 免疫接种是防制此病的重要方法，在育成期用弱毒苗点眼、滴鼻免疫，可收到理想的效果。

label: [{"start":1,"end":3,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":40,"end":48,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":78,"end":86,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 因疫苗中的含毒量、接种途径和疫苗毒株的不同，免疫期不同，从6周到1年不等，所以，鸡传染性喉气管炎流行区域内的鸡场在50日龄和100日龄2次免疫，基本上可控制鸡传染性喉气管炎的流行。

label: [{"start":3,"end":13,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 在使用鸡传染性喉气管炎疫苗的实践中，有些鸡场存在着恐惧心理，流传着“不使用不得，使用就得”的说法。实际上这是一种错觉。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 不使用疫苗免疫，一有流行就难以逃脱；使用过疫苗之后，即使当时有轻微反应，但不会酿成大祸。

label: [{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 至于使用后造成的损失绝非疫苗问题，而是免疫方法不对，免疫的时间不对，免疫操作不严谨，人员、用具、场地消毒不严造成的。

label: [{"start":4,"end":5,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":19,"end":20,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":58,"end":66,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 非疫区的鸡缺乏免疫力，尽管疫苗是弱毒，鸡的感染力也很强，所以免疫过程中散毒是重要的原因，如1996年冬至1997年夏鸡传染性喉气管炎流行时，有些鸡场就免遭其害，保护率达95%～99%。

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"疫苗免疫","labels":["control"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 鸡传染性喉气管炎对养鸡业危害甚大，用疫苗免疫是不可缺少的保护措施。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"疱疹病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":22,"end":33,"text":"高度接触性呼吸道传染病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":16,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"急性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"喘气","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":43,"end":50,"text":"咳出血样渗出物","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 传染性喉气管炎是由疱疹病毒引起鸡的一种急性、高度接触性呼吸道传染病，以呼吸困难、喘气、咳出血样渗出物为特征。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":28,"text":"产蛋量下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 传染性喉气管炎由于造成明显的呼吸困难而致死以及产蛋量下降，给养鸡业带来了巨大的损失。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":18,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":44,"end":47,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 传染性喉气管炎有明显的宿主特异性，鸡为主要的自然宿主，各年龄均可感染，但以4~10月龄的成年鸡尤为严重且多表现典型症状。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"野鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"幼火鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"禽类","labels":["type"]}]
text: 野鸡、鹌鹑、孔雀和幼火鸡也可感染，其他禽类和哺乳类动物不感染。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"带毒鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"康复鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":34,"text":"上呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"眼内","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡和带毒鸡是主要的传染源，约有2%的康复鸡能带毒2年，可经上呼吸道和眼内感染。

label: [{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"强毒疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 污染的垫料和用具也能带毒。强毒疫苗接种鸡群后，能造成散毒污染环境。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":50,"end":57,"text":"传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":58,"end":59,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 传染性喉气管炎传播迅速，一年四季均可发生，发病率可高达90%～100%,死亡率5%~50%不等，耐过传染性喉气管炎的鸡具有长期免疫力。

label: [{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 自然感染的潜伏期为6~12天，人工气管内接种的潜伏期为2~4天。

label: [{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"喉气管型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"急性型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (1)急性型(喉气管型)。主要在成年鸡发生，传播迅速，短期内全群感染。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"精神沉郁","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"厌食","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":48,"end":55,"text":"咳嗽多呈痉挛性","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":30,"text":"呼吸时突然向上向前伸头张口","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":29,"end":30,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"喘气","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"伴有鸣音","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":57,"end":64,"text":"咳出带血的黏液","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":65,"end":68,"text":"血凝块","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 病鸡精神沉郁、厌食、呼吸困难，每次呼吸时突然向上向前伸头张口并伴有鸣音和喘气声，喘气和咳嗽严重，咳嗽多呈痉挛性，并咳出带血的黏液或血凝块。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"头颈蜷缩","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"嘴喙下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"眼全闭","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":45,"text":"黏膜上附有黄色或带血的浓稠黏液或豆渣样物质","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"黄色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"喉部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"眼","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"嘴喙","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":5,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":3,"end":4,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"蜷缩","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"浓稠黏液","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":45,"text":"豆渣样物质","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 病重者头颈蜷缩，嘴喙下垂，眼全闭。检查喉部，可见黏膜上附有黄色或带血的浓稠黏液或豆渣样物质。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":31,"end":32,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 产蛋鸡的产蛋量下降约12%。病程一般为10~14天，康复后有的鸡可能成为带毒者。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"温和型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"眼结膜型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":35,"end":45,"text":"眼角积聚泡沫性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"流泪","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":49,"end":54,"text":"眼结膜发炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"发炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":45,"text":"泡沫性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":61,"text":"不断用爪抓眼","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":62,"end":68,"text":"眼睛轻度充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":64,"end":68,"text":"轻度充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":69,"end":76,"text":"眼睑肿胀和粘连","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":74,"end":76,"text":"粘连","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":71,"end":73,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":80,"end":82,"text":"失明","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"眼角","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":49,"end":52,"text":"眼结膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":58,"end":59,"text":"爪","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":60,"end":61,"text":"眼","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"眼睛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":69,"end":71,"text":"眼睑","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (2)温和型(眼结膜型)。主要在30～40日龄的鸡发生，症状较轻。病初眼角积聚泡沫性分泌物，流泪，眼结膜发炎，不断用爪抓眼，眼睛轻度充血，眼睑肿胀和粘连，严重的失明。

label: [{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"角膜混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"溃疡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":25,"text":"浆液性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"眶下窦肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":36,"end":40,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":43,"end":47,"text":"生长迟缓","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"角膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":25,"text":"鼻腔有持续性的浆液性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"眶下窦","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 病的后期角膜混浊、溃疡，鼻腔有持续性的浆液性分泌物，眶下窦肿胀。病鸡偶见呼吸困难，表现生长迟缓，死亡率为5%左右。

label: [{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"喉头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":17,"text":"喙","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":28,"text":"附有带血的黏液","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 病理变化主要集中在喉头和气管，在喙的周围常附有带血的黏液。

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"喉头和气管黏膜肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":31,"text":"气管腔内常充满血凝块","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":31,"text":"血凝块","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"黏液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":44,"text":"淡黄色干酪样渗出物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":38,"text":"淡黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":45,"end":48,"text":"气管塞","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"喉头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"气管黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":24,"text":"气管腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 喉头和气管黏膜肿胀、充血、出血，甚至坏死；气管腔内常充满血凝块、黏液、淡黄色干酪样渗出物或气管塞。

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"渗出液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"炎症扩散","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"气管下部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"肺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"气囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 有些病例，渗出液出现于气管下部，并使炎症扩散到支气管、肺和气囊。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"温和型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":24,"text":"眼结膜和眶下窦上皮水肿和充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":13,"text":"眼结膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":19,"text":"眶下窦上皮","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"角膜混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":37,"text":"眶下窦肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":38,"end":44,"text":"有干酪样物质","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"角膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":32,"end":35,"text":"眶下窦","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 温和型病例一般只出现眼结膜和眶下窦上皮水肿和充血，有时角膜混浊，眶下窦肿胀并有干酪样物质。

label: [{"start":19,"end":20,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 根据典型症状和病理变化不难做出诊断，若鸡日龄较小或症状、病理变化不明显，尚需进一步进行分离病毒和血清学试验以确诊。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"免疫接种","labels":["control"]},{"start":7,"end":14,"text":"传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"弱毒疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 免疫接种是防制传染性喉气管炎的重要方法，弱毒疫苗首次免疫在28日龄左右，二次免疫在首次免疫后6周，即70日龄左右进行。

label: [{"start":5,"end":13,"text":"眶下窦与鼻内滴注","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"点眼","labels":["control"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"饮水免疫","labels":["control"]},{"start":15,"end":16,"text":"眼","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":10,"text":"鼻","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"眶下窦","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 免疫方法有眶下窦与鼻内滴注、点眼及饮水免疫等。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"结膜炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"鼻炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":37,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"死亡","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 鸡群接种后可产生一定的疫苗反应，轻者出现结膜炎和鼻炎，严重者可引起呼吸困难甚至死亡。

label: [{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":7,"end":20,"text":"疫苗必须严格按使用说明进行","labels":["control"]},{"start":31,"end":41,"text":"做好兽医卫生管理工作","labels":["control"]}]
text: 因此，所使用的疫苗必须严格按使用说明进行，并结合当地情况。同时做好兽医卫生管理工作。

label: [{"start":5,"end":18,"text":"传染性喉气管炎与鸡痘二联苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 此外，使用传染性喉气管炎与鸡痘二联苗效果也不错。

label: [{"start":5,"end":11,"text":"综合防制措施","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":21,"end":27,"text":"改善鸡舍通风","labels":["control"]},{"start":28,"end":34,"text":"注意环境卫生","labels":["control"]},{"start":35,"end":40,"text":"不引进病鸡","labels":["control"]},{"start":42,"end":52,"text":"严格执行消毒卫生措施","labels":["control"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 同时应采取综合防制措施，平时加强饲养管理，改善鸡舍通风，注意环境卫生，不引进病鸡，并严格执行消毒卫生措施。

label: [{"start":2,"end":9,"text":"传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"杀菌剂","labels":["drug"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"泰乐加","labels":["drug"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"链霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"氯霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":42,"end":45,"text":"氟哌酸","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 发生传染性喉气管炎后，用杀菌剂每日进行1~2次消毒，并辅之以泰乐加、链霉素、氯霉素、氟哌酸等药物治疗以防细菌继发感染。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性喉气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"中草药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":47,"end":51,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"特效药物","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 传染性喉气管炎目前尚无特效药物治疗，但在临床上使用某些中草药有一定的辅助治疗作用，可减轻病鸡的呼吸困难。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"麻黄","labels":["drug"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"杏仁","labels":["drug"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"厚朴","labels":["drug"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"陈皮","labels":["drug"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"甘草","labels":["drug"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"苏子","labels":["drug"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"半夏","labels":["drug"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"前胡","labels":["drug"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"桑皮","labels":["drug"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"木香","labels":["drug"]},{"start":41,"end":47,"text":"取药汁拌饲料","labels":["control"]},{"start":48,"end":52,"text":"饮水喂鸡","labels":["control"]},{"start":51,"end":52,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":55,"end":56,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":67,"end":69,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":59,"end":64,"text":"混合干药粉","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 麻黄、杏仁、厚朴、陈皮、甘草各1份。苏子、半夏、前胡、桑皮、木香各2份，混合煎水，取药汁拌饲料或饮水喂鸡，每只鸡平均喂混合干药粉5g,雏鸡减半，效果确实。
